  • Field Details

    • CONF_MASTER_PASSWORD

      static final String CONF_MASTER_PASSWORD
      Configuration key for masterPassword. It may be present, if SecDispatcher could obtain it, but presence is optional. Still, dispatcher may throw and fail the operation if it requires it.
